{"tid":350444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台仔就不能上網 台電正式亮今年首顆「紅燈」","createTime":"2017-08-07T08:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T10:58:31.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a1e355d02a8420e2491069954b06d0229864b67","tid":350444,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:50:13.000Z","msg":"今天氣候炎熱，氣溫再創新高，據中央氣象局最新觀測資料，台北市在下午1時57分出現38.5℃高溫，打破台北今年最高溫紀錄，也是今年全台最高溫紀錄，這也是台北站歷史8月份第四高溫紀錄。用電量也大增，用電量一度達到限電警戒紅燈的範圍˙。今天下午1時40分尖峰用電達到3604.3萬瓩，備轉容量僅62萬瓩；下午2時30分尖峰用電達到3586.4萬瓩，今日尖峰供電能力為3666.5萬瓩，備轉容量已低於90萬瓩，只有約83.8萬瓩，依標準已達到紅燈警戒，但目前台電官網顯示還僅在供電警戒的橘燈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/recommend/20170807/1177168\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Frecommend%2F20170807%2F1177168&d=7%2FtOmr58GaXyuYwrXBw2xZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=a45aaac2\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/recommend/20170807/1177168</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熱到咁，限電暴動似"},{"pid":"860cd2c7fc75c4635c7b400557f1276e6e4b088e","tid":350444,"uid":39012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:54:19.000Z","msg":"反對核電的惡果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d067e47081d1a672fbddd47c182d4e04b4128f9","tid":350444,"uid":109462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反對核電的惡果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n然而蔡英文總統仲着緊長袖衫開冷氣睇棒球賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知民進黨幾時表演用愛發電<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecf8f67271d8e4f41b2edffdf3eab30533223b0","tid":350444,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:59:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反對核電的惡果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class