r />\n中國人玩政治仲留係幼稚園水平"},{"pid":"1f5c2e91f7ad149f55a7737a6c3465f4621c089e","tid":350444,"uid":13149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人做國家元首，無好下場<br />\n德國係例外</blockquote><br />\n德國咪又係玩死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905624170560f39789f780aba234eb3ab11a940a","tid":350444,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>女人做國家元首，無好下場<br />\n德國係例外</blockquote><br />\n德國咪又係玩死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其他地方唔知，但起碼中國歷史上女人得勢嘅時間都唔好過；你睇漢代呂后、唐代武韋之亂、清代慈禧、紅朝江青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad0e51cc8ae058f3ca392f5d3736bef117adfb6","tid":350444,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"以為又vpn"},{"pid":"21abc64754163901af567afeb722fe64bc1a451e","tid":350444,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:57:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人做國家元首，無好下場<br />\n德國係例外</blockquote><br />\n默克爾係政府首腦，唔係國家元首。"},{"pid":"e830b65a20921c7d155f5c6bc17076ba22b5b550","tid":350444,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HN1dTcL_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=high\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHN1dTcL_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dhigh&h=4dabfb11&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g